===[[Pokémon GO]]===
{{main|Style (GO)}}
For the release of {{g|Sword and Shield}}, Victor's outfit was released as free style options in [[Pokémon GO]]. For each release of the [[Pokémon Sword and Shield Expansion Pass]], style options based on outfits from [[The Isle of Armor]] and [[The Crown Tundra]] have also been made for free.
